numafung [ nʊmɑː fʊŋ ] is a 2004 limbu language film that portrays the culture and tradition of the limbu community .   it is directed by nabin subba .   the film was screened at the thirteenth finnish indigenous film festival .   the lead characters in the movie are anupama subba , niwahangma limbu , prem subba , alok nembang and ramesh singhak .   numafung means a " beautiful flower " in the limbu language .   the majority of shooting took place at panchthar , nepal sikkim and assam .